This project is built to run as a single instance for a company.

There is no multi-tennancy.

The Company details are stored in a singleton style settings model.

Use only standard ASCII punctuation. Never use curly/smart quotes (e.g. ' or ' for apostrophe; use '), em-dashes (use a hyphen), or other Unicode punctuation. This applies to all generated or edited text, including comments, docs, and commit messages.
